  "detailed_description": "In a city devastated by the cataclysmic upheaval, you emerge as the only survivor in the nightmare of a terrible swarm of insects. Survive the onslaught through the devastation and reclaim the city from the insect-infested horrors.<br><br>There are limited resources on the map, and they are hidden throughout the map. To defeat all enemies, <strong>plan well</strong> and destroy them!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/9b8b68f306c4808f538d427a03187470.poster.avif?t=1713949105\" width=512 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/9b8b68f306c4808f538d427a03187470.webm?t=1713949105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/9b8b68f306c4808f538d427a03187470.mp4?t=1713949105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The only survivor</strong></h2>You are the only survivor of the city.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/4cb3327f314957d6dd8620d14034f88c.poster.avif?t=1713949105\" width=512 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/4cb3327f314957d6dd8620d14034f88c.webm?t=1713949105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/4cb3327f314957d6dd8620d14034f88c.mp4?t=1713949105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Threat</strong></h2>Every creature in this city is trying to kill you.<br>Every enemy has a different pattern of behavior, and once they've seen you, they'll chase you to death.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/7d2d7c843fc112a6f8effce6a59b94b3.poster.avif?t=1713949105\" width=512 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/7d2d7c843fc112a6f8effce6a59b94b3.webm?t=1713949105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/7d2d7c843fc112a6f8effce6a59b94b3.mp4?t=1713949105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exploration</strong></h2>Get the items you need from each building in the city.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/05d15a6f4f6c0946a8149b213787c79b.poster.avif?t=1713949105\" width=512 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/05d15a6f4f6c0946a8149b213787c79b.webm?t=1713949105\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2921960/extras/05d15a6f4f6c0946a8149b213787c79b.mp4?t=1713949105\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>DEBUG</strong></h2>Unconditionally Survive! Get rid of all the insects in the city!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Estimated play time</strong></h2>120min ~ <br><br><br>It's a one-person development, so the update may be slow.<br>Please give me your feedback at <a href=\"mailto:sejongyun7@gmail.com\">sejongyun7@gmail.com</a> .<br>All the necessary assets were purchased from Marketplace.",
